{"type": "article", "id": 24008, "title": "像纸片一样的极简烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-17T07:00:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607124748en8rPEIt5uD0dVFz.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这几乎是最简单的烛台，它像一个微微上翘的纸片。它是铝制的，两头都带着可插蜡烛的圆孔。其中一头有些微的上扬和折痕，它套在下一个蜡烛上，围合成一个三角形或正方形，就像微微浮起的波纹，在简单和优雅中透着一些趣味。单个售价 35.62 美元起，<a href=\"https://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/wave-aluminium-pale-green-candle-holder/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124745ZMmedEoOv90cQbGW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124746NiyLXah9vB6rcuFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124747wX1ATnosPIpmbjHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124747hB153x4fYKRrFAXw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124747rET1w4H8kqvh63iM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71382979\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}